headline: F5 Redefines ADC for the AI Era
summary: SEATTLE, February 11, 2025--F5 (NASDAQ: FFIV) today outlined its vision on how Application Delivery Controllers (ADCs) must transform to meet the extraordinary demands of modern and AI-powered applications. With a platform-based approach that delivers flexibility in form factor, management capabilities, and advanced control over every aspect of application security and delivery, F5 is leading the way and developing this next generation of ADCs.
